				<title>RabbitMQ（一）：核心概念与架构</title>
				<link>https://liwenqikeep.github.io/posts/rabbitmq%E4%B8%80%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E6%A6%82%E5%BF%B5%E4%B8%8E%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84/</link>
